dc_title_s: Transit Stops - Itinerary Stops Only - Archive: Minnesota
dc_description_s: The Transit Stops Archive layer contains over 14,000 active transit stops that are part of a transit route itinerary in the Twin Cities seven county metropolitan area. The to and from dates represent when that geometry and attribute information was valid. The earliest version of the Transit Stop itinerary is March 25, 2017.  The dataset includes attributes from the primary transit stop database maintained for MetroTransit and for customer information for other transit provider transit services. The locations are mapped referencing NCompass Technologies Inc. street centerline network along with streets generated internally at MetroTransit.
